d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d65dc36a93d329781106b0af69bf6820963150d","tid":161912,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:27:29.000Z","msg":"正常保安發現賊 應該去報警 等警方處理<br />\n警犬有槍同訓練  班老野睇得多電影先會自己上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得把電筒 點同賊打"},{"pid":"3cf315d8fb02acd98e15d7aa7eb4413f4d914355","tid":161912,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:27:41.000Z","msg":"宜家大家都知保安幾盡責呢"},{"pid":"df0f2505583247773ddcf74b09693c67476de379","tid":161912,"uid":38476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:30:52.000Z","msg":"Respect<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb37321400504e27fa93a93668297fa18d9e9c46","tid":161912,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:32:28.000Z","msg":"此人不下呂布"},{"pid":"81ed637c0c75a5fca7ba442173358fd413a7fa38","tid":161912,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:44:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33ec7237986189ac466e69c80896c103c556c8b5","tid":161912,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"三英戰呂布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係耆英喎"},{"pid":"4f9786f75f9a3014c6864343335fef1206567837","tid":161912,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071296db8148059209e8209375d26a3e4f6080b7","tid":161912,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:48:47.000Z","msg":"保安唔係浪得虛名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji